Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你該明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是十字教最大宗派
